# Platform — Internal Tenant Provisioning
# UC-024: Platform operator provisions a new tenant
#
# Prerequisites:
#   1. pnpm infra:up           (start PostgreSQL + Pub/Sub emulator)
#   2. pnpm --filter @ikaro/backend run migration:run
#   3. pnpm --filter @ikaro/backend run dev
#
# REST Client reads PLATFORM_ADMIN_KEY from apps/backend/.env automatically.
# Switch environment (bottom-right VS Code status bar): select "local"

@baseUrl     = {{backendUrl}}
@adminKey    = {{$dotenv PLATFORM_ADMIN_KEY}}
@internalKey = {{$dotenv INTERNAL_API_KEY}}
@authHeader  = Bearer {{adminKey}}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HAPPY PATH
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Provision a new tenant (minimal — timezone defaults to America/Sao_Paulo)
# @name provisionTenant
POST {{baseUrl}}/internal/tenants
Authorization: {{authHeader}}
X-Internal-Key: {{internalKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Lavacar Belo Horizonte",
  "slug": "lavacar-bh",
  "adminEmail": "admin@lavacar-bh.com.br"
}

###

### Provision a new tenant (explicit timezone)
POST {{baseUrl}}/internal/tenants
Authorization: {{authHeader}}
X-Internal-Key: {{internalKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Lavacar Manaus",
  "slug": "lavacar-manaus",
  "adminEmail": "admin@lavacar-manaus.com.br",
  "timezone": "America/Manaus"
}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ERROR CASES — useful to verify guard + validation are working
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 401 — Missing X-Internal-Key (global guard)
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/tenants/by-slug/lavacar-bh

###

### 401 — Missing Authorization header (PlatformAdminGuard — X-Internal-Key present)
POST {{baseUrl}}/internal/tenants
X-Internal-Key: {{internalKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test",
  "slug": "test",
  "adminEmail": "test@test.com"
}

###

### 401 — Wrong API key (PlatformAdminGuard — X-Internal-Key present)
POST {{baseUrl}}/internal/tenants
Authorization: Bearer wrong-key
X-Internal-Key: {{internalKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test",
  "slug": "test",
  "adminEmail": "test@test.com"
}

###

### 400 — Invalid slug format (uppercase + space)
POST {{baseUrl}}/internal/tenants
Authorization: {{authHeader}}
X-Internal-Key: {{internalKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test",
  "slug": "Invalid Slug!",
  "adminEmail": "test@test.com"
}

###

### 400 — Invalid email
POST {{baseUrl}}/internal/tenants
Authorization: {{authHeader}}
X-Internal-Key: {{internalKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test",
  "slug": "valid-slug",
  "adminEmail": "not-an-email"
}

###

### 400 — Invalid IANA timezone
POST {{baseUrl}}/internal/tenants
Authorization: {{authHeader}}
X-Internal-Key: {{internalKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test",
  "slug": "valid-slug-2",
  "adminEmail": "test@test.com",
  "timezone": "Europe/Not-A-Zone"
}

###

### 409 — Duplicate slug (run the happy-path request first, then this one)
POST {{baseUrl}}/internal/tenants
Authorization: {{authHeader}}
X-Internal-Key: {{internalKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Duplicate",
  "slug": "lavacar-bh",
  "adminEmail": "other@lavacar-bh.com.br"
}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# READ — Tenant lookup by ID (BFF-internal, no auth guard)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Happy path — get tenant info by ID (run provisionTenant above first)
@tenantId = {{provisionTenant.response.body.tenantId}}
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/tenants/{{tenantId}}
X-Internal-Key: {{internalKey}}

###

### 404 — Unknown tenant ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/tenants/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
X-Internal-Key: {{internalKey}}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# READ — Published hotsites listing (M12-S09 — backs apps/web sitemap.xml)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### List active tenants with a published hotsite — { items: [{ slug, updatedAt }] }
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/tenants/published-hotsites
X-Internal-Key: {{internalKey}}

###

### 401 — Missing X-Internal-Key (global guard)
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/tenants/published-hotsites
